, \"rank\": 1.0399468375603945e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meadow will be among the first out on course at 8am, with Maguire due to tee off around 11.17am.\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Maguire_Cup\", \"score\": 0.996927923724406, \"rank\": 0.003081543010744266, \"text\": \"Maguire\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Maguire_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Maguire_Cup\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rhasidat Adelekeis set to run in the first of the women's 400m semi-finals.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is the only Irish athlete to make it through to the semis after her team-mates Sharlene Mawdsley and Sophie Becker failed to come through the heats and repechage.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999895780758498, \"rank\": 1.0399468375603945e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 588, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\", \"score\": 0.9999944927823652, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sophie Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, before that,Sarah Lavinwill be the first Irish athlete out on the track to compete for a place in the women's 100m hurdles.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r