tages.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The medal race in the sailing is also taking place with Finn Lynch hoping for a strong finish.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"score\": 0.9928881143377358, \"rank\": 0.005498422958822904, \"text\": \"Finn\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He can not come away with a medal.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(In order of start time)  0800-1700Women's singles: Leona Maguire and Stephanie Meadow  Stephanie Meadowtee-time 0800with Perrine Delacour of France and Manon De Roey of Belgium.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leona_Maguire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leona Maguire\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leona_Maguire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leona_Maguire\"}, {\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Meadow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephanie Meadow\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Meadow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Meadow\"}, {\"begin\": 1519, \"end\": 1528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.987851463908495, \"rank\": 0.012267100231763375, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource